hopobject.body: Good crew it's cool :) is noosa yoghurt healthy for you The couple first set eyes on each other in 2001 at Scotland's University of St. Andrews. Both lived in St. Salvator's Hall as first-year history of art students — although William later switched his field to geography. Middleton was a sporty girl from the English countryside who admits she 'went bright red' and 'scuttled off feeling very shy' the first time she met the prince. One of the most charming newly revealed photos shows the happy couple on the day of their graduation, June 23, 2005, from St. Andrew's University where they met.
